00:45:50.390 --> 00:45:52.250
it's a wonderful
puzzle for me too,

00:45:52.250 --> 00:45:56.660
to try to bring Chinese
poetry into, you know,

00:45:56.660 --> 00:45:59.120
into the western world.

00:45:59.120 --> 00:46:03.200
&gt;&gt; Ron Charles: It is--
it is wonderful for us.

00:46:03.200 --> 00:46:05.730
Here is a poem that
