00:49:50.860 --> 00:49:54.100
The dog is barking at the door.

00:49:54.100 --> 00:49:57.740
What does the proud beast know?

00:49:57.740 --> 00:50:02.050
Who is both master and intruder?

00:50:02.050 --> 00:50:05.040
Whose bloody handprint
on the wall?

00:50:05.040 --> 00:50:08.370
Whose revolver in
the dishwasher?

00:50:08.370 --> 00:50:12.940
The neighbors won't
heed her alarm.

00:50:12.940 --> 00:50:21.720
She keeps barking, barking,
bent on saving their kind.

00:50:22.850 --> 00:50:25.880
I-- I think domestic
violence will do us in.

